9. Nd4
{ The centralized knight stops ...d5 as our pawn on c6 would be undefended. }
9... O-O 10. Nf5 { A blunt Knight leap, which runs into an obvious reply. }
10... d5 { 10...d6  should be the same. } 11. exd6 Bxd6 12. Nxd6 cxd6
{ Black is completely fine.   12...Nxd6  was also OK but it's certainly more practical to improve our pawn structure. }
