10... Nc5 { Black starts by maneuvering the knight to an optimal position. }
11. Be3 Ne6 12. Nd4
{ This is the main move. It's a very direct approach. White again stops the ...d5 break and a certain ingenuity is required from Black. }
12... Rb8
