{ A strong novelty which rejuvenates the line. Now a7 is not hanging and we get a bit of space on the queenside. As it is a novelty that's a completely new territory and there are no games. We did a match @@StartBracket@@8 games, 5 minutes per game@@EndBracket@@ between Stockfish 12 and itself and all the games finished with a draw. }
