Qe4
{ White's activity is sufficient to keep the balance but no more than that. }
17... Bxb2 18. Rb1 Be5
{ It's objectively equal but probably White needs to be more careful.   Also  18...Nf6  19.Qb4  Nd5  leads to equality. }
