1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. d3
{ The so-called anti-Berlin, which was long considered completetely harmless but has been gaining more and more popularity in recent years due to futility of White's attempts in the Berlin Endgame. }
