{ More accurate than  19...Kb7  , which runs into  20.b4 } 20. b4 Rde8
{ 20...a5  immediately is less accurate due to  21.bxa5  d4  22.Ne2  d3  23.Nf4  and Black doesn't have the ...d2 and ...Re1+ resource. }
21. Bf3 a5
{ The point of putting the king on  b8  is that now White doesn't have  22.b5  because of  22...d4  and there is no  23.bxc6+.  While entire idea behind playing ...a5 is to exchange pawns so that White is left with a weak pawn on the queenside. }
22. bxa5 d4 *

