{ This strange move has been popular recently, but it is more of a surprise weapon than anything else. }
8... Qe6 { Preparing ...d6 and ...Bxd6 or ...Bb4+ in case of c4. } 9. g3 d6
{ The easiest answer. } 10. c4 Nb6 11. exd6 Bxd6
{ Taking with the bishop is better, because piece activity is more important than structure. The position does not require further analysis, since Black is already slightly better thanks to his better development. }
