{ Of course Black is also on top after 12...0-0. } 13. Nxd2 O-O 14. O-O-O Re8
15. f4
{ The opening was a clear failure for White in Nakamura-Robson, Saint Louis 2018. Black's best move is: }
15... d5 { with a clear advantage. } *

