{ White is badly tied up and Black's pieces are extremely effective. All the engines give clear advantage to Black but it's a complex battle ahead. Sample line goes: }
17. Kh1 Qd7 18. b4 Bf8 19. a3 f6 20. Bc1 Kb8
{ Black is ready to continue with ...g5 or ...c5 , depending on circumstances. White's pieces are too cramped and pinned to generate meaningful counterplay. }
