{ 21...Qxf3+?  22.Qg2  is wrong,   as is  21...Bf4?  22.d6!   or  21...Re8?  22.Qg2  and 23.Qg4+!  The text move does not allow White queen to g4, e.g. }
22. Qg2 f5
{ Black has the advantage but it's very complex so you can play around with the engine. }
