9. e5 dxc3 10. d4 Bf8
{ Preparing to take on  f6  with the queen. After  10...Be7  11.exf6  Bxf6  12.Qe1+  Black is not as much better as in the text continuation. }
11. exf6 Qxf6 12. Qe1+ Be7 13. Qxc3 O-O
{ Due to his horribly miscplaced bishop on a4, White will face an uphill struggle for survival. }
