{ White does not have a good follow-up to his reckless pawn storm.   We had some other sensible moves at this point but for example  13...O-O  14.g5  is just messy  while here we are safely preparing ...Qc8 or ...c6 fighting for important squares and we are not afraid of g5 with the rook on h8. }
