Nxe5 11. Rxe5 Be6 12. Bxd5
{ A sad necessity. Black was threatening ...Bf6  and   12.d4  fails to  12...Nxc3 }
12... Bxd5 13. d4 c6
{ With ...Bd6 coming, Black has more than enough play for the pawn. } *

