12... Bh5 13. c3
{ 13.Bd5  This was slightly more tenable, although White would still be in dire straits:  13...O-O-O  14.O-O  Rxd5  15.Ng3  f4  16.Nge4  Qh4  17.Kh1  Re8  18.d3  Nf5  Black is winning, e.g.  19.Bd2  Bxf2  20.Rxf2  Rxe4  21.dxe4  Qxf2  22.exd5  Nh4!  23.Qg1  Qxd2-+ }
13... fxe4 14. Nxe4 Qh4+ 15. Ng3
{ 15.g3  Nxf3+  16.Qxf3  Bxf3  17.gxh4  Bxh1-+  led to a decisive material advantage for Black. }
15... O-O-O 16. Kf1 Bxf3 17. gxf3 Qh3+ 18. Kf2 Nxb3+
